name: Google Drive File Stream
desc: Client for the Google Drive storage service
caveats:
RENAME WARNING

`google-drive-file-stream` will be renamed `google-drive`.
In the meantime, `google-drive-file-stream` will install `google-drive` for you as a dependency, but you should update your scripts.

We’re aware this solution is subpar. If you’d like to help us improve it,
we accept PRs and need the equivalent of formula_renames.json for casks: https://docs.brew.sh/Rename-A-Formula

To migrate now, do:
  brew uninstall google-drive-file-stream
  brew install google-drive
